Mozambique country borders

country.Rd

Mozambique country borders

country

Format

A SpatialPolygonsDataFrame object containing country borders of Mozambique

VariablesDescription
Shape_LengShape length
Shape_AreaShape area
ADM0_ENAdministrative area level 0 name in English
ADM0_PTAdministrative area level 0 name in Portuguese
ADM0_PCODEAdministrative area level 0 postal code
ADM0_REFAdministrative area level 0 reference
ADM0ALT1ENAdministrative area level 0 alternative English name 1
ADM0ALT2ENAdministrative area level 0 alternative English name 2
ADM0ALT1PTAdministrative area level 0 alternative Portuguese name 1
ADM0ALT2PTAdministrative area level 0 alternative Portuguese name 2
dateDate created
validOnData valid on
validToData valid to

Source

https://data.humdata.org/dataset/mozambique-administrative-levels-0-3
